{"tid":608932,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"想請教養盾臂巴絲","createTime":"2018-03-28T14:46:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-31T13:28:56.000Z","uid":158857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"40166fb45aab042af453d95c74d7b79ce2e7bcb2","tid":608932,"uid":158857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T14:46:11.000Z","msg":"朋友搬屋，冇地方養，隻盾臂3-4歲<br />\n本身都有領養左隻巴西，不過盾臂真係唔敢亂黎。<br />\n我住私樓頂層連天台，天台有電插燈，整間小龜屋應該冇問題。問題係天台會同其他住戶對分，閒說盾臂好鍾意食屎，玩屎。請問係咪堅係玩得好勁，因為我驚太臭比人投訴，同埋佢地痾屎會唔會好密，因為我想半放養，日間由佢係我天台自己玩，夜晚先搬佢返有圍欄的龜屋，但如果佢成日痾，又鍾意踩屎醬，個天台日日要大洗都似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n請問有冇巴絲可以分享下戶外養盾臂的心得，同間屋d整好"},{"pid":"a60c5d7db91b4a465498be4be87dcdb95df013be","tid":608932,"uid":58445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T05:27:34.000Z","msg":"有屎佢就會食 食到成手成嘴都係 周圍hi"},{"pid":"0276e66e8d962bad52071d529b8e8fd544329728","tid":608932,"uid":158857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a60c5d7db91b4a465498be4be87dcdb95df013be","tid":608932,"uid":58445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T05:27:34.000Z","msg":"有屎佢就會食 食到成手成嘴都係 周圍hi"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T06:28:43.000Z","msg":"佢地開大次數頻唔頻密，閒說可以訓練佢浸暖水先痾，堅唔堅？"},{"pid":"7d42181e7708ff46a38c78e07a7e27d2c0f978d1","tid":608932,"uid":59684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T23:43:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 🐢"},{"pid":"f27125fd1709e3d7a0e2c7ec397f8206efcb4e45","tid":608932,"uid":1262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0276e66e8d962bad52071d529b8e8fd544329728","tid":608932,"uid":158857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a60c5d7db91b4a465498be4be87dcdb95df013be","tid":608932,"uid":58445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T05:27:34.000Z","msg":"有屎佢